data.clean_description: God damn whitey does it again. This Sweet Skunk Cake Batter is the tip top of the extract game right now , fluffy dry and oh so tasty. Cake Batter is a BHO product similar to Shatter however it undergoes some extra processing and what comes out is this amazing terpy dab cookie. Pictures up soon.
data.name: 1 Gram Sweet Skunk Cake Batter
